name: Vortex in a Jar (1 of 1)
description:
Vortex in a Jar💫

Own your very 1st Vortex encased inside of a jar made of stardust.

The tale goes... 
Whomever owns this Vortex is granted unlimited time. 
As long as the Vortex spins and swirls, 
your stars are sure to align.
It's mystical & magical, yet very very small.
But you shall never let size fool you, 
for it could destroy us all.

*Includes High-Res MP4 + Gif Version*
Art by: @SolarKittyn🐦
